beer.beer_description: Help us celebrate our years of brewing with this American pale ale! It’s a beer brewed in the spirit of celebration, highly hopped and full bodied. Munich malt and caramel steam malt lend lush colour and subtle biscuit and toffee notes, while the hops deliver the goods with aromas of pine, stonefruit, and citrus. Happy birthday to Hawkers!
